## 11. Image uploads & storage

1. Use Laravel storage:

   ```bash
   php artisan storage:link
   ```
2. In controller `store()`:

```php
$path = $request->file('image')->store('products','public');
$product->image_path = $path;
```

3. In Blade: `<img src="{{ asset('storage/' . $product->image_path) }}" />`

